    "description": "<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2356040/extras/2f4f9b35eca1e7730667739244f40ad1.poster.avif?t=1768856487\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2356040/extras/2f4f9b35eca1e7730667739244f40ad1.webm?t=1768856487\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2356040/extras/2f4f9b35eca1e7730667739244f40ad1.mp4?t=1768856487\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Reefland Odyssey is an exciting adventure game where you navigate a ship through the vast ocean and clean up the pollution that threatens the health of the marine ecosystem. As you sail through the beautiful and challenging waters of the reefland, you'll face obstacles like whirlpools and storms. But with your keen navigation skills and garbage collecting tools, you'll be able to overcome these challenges and make the ocean a cleaner, healthier place. So climb aboard your ship and embark on a journey of ocean preservation.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2356040/extras/93bc65f21aca8886cebf7574b7f6d079.poster.avif?t=1768856487\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2356040/extras/93bc65f21aca8886cebf7574b7f6d079.webm?t=1768856487\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2356040/extras/93bc65f21aca8886cebf7574b7f6d079.mp4?t=1768856487\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
